  "note": "Triceratops is a Large Fighter. (She can attack up to 2 spaces away.)\n--------------------\nVersion 2.3 - Remove the scheme card \"Closer than the she appears\" as observed not thematic to the hero; Change the Stampede atk card to a scheme card; Added the Fatal Struggle atk card as a new attack card with 3 copies for drawing power and also thematic to the Trike. Increase the BOOST value of Momentous Shift versatile card from 1 to 2. Wording update on special ability just added She can attack up to 2 spaces away and the removed ability name. Slight buff on Herbivorous Dinosaurs scheme, adding optional choice in doing both draw card and health recovery effect. Change image address of the card back art and card arts.\n--------------------\nMy First custom character. Inspired on Jurassic Universe's Triceratops. Disclaimer on the fanart and images not my property, just edited them at photopea.com\n--------------------\nSpecial thanks to the Discord community: @Retinoid ; @ComeFrank; @Basedana ; @Fracture; @DoubleCrunch; @Cviko5691; @MrR3dstoneGhost002\n--------------------\nTTS json file: https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1hn7mEOl5XGeojF6CC6DREJu6YeoIJWRV",
